<col>@046b shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i mdzod kyi lde mig ces bya ba kha che'i mkhan po bla ma dharma shr'is mdzad pa rdzogs so 'phags pa bsdud pa'i gdams gdams ngag 'di byang chub sa'i snying po dpal 'bum stengs kyi gtsug lag khang gsar du bzhengs pa'i dus su slob dpon chen po byang chub sems dpa' dang gdan 'dzom nas shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di @047a * bsgyur cing bka' stsal te ston sgom spag ma gsum gyis zhu ba phul` dge slong dri ma med pas yon bdag mdzad nas mkhas pa chen po pa reg lo ts'a bas sems can kyi don du bsgyur pa'o`` `` smras pa dus gsum sangs rgyas 'di la brten 'byung phyir rgyal ba rang nyid yang yang bsngags pa dang yang yang yangs su @047b gtang dang gled gzhi sogs rnam grangs du mas gzhan las khyad 'phags gsungs shin tu 'phrad dka' gong na med pa 'di yal par 'dor ba dpyod ldan su zhig yod lan gcig thos pa'i rten bzang thob dus 'dir thar ba'i sa bon ci thub bzhag dgos lags 'dir 'bad dge ba'i rtsa ba ci mchis pa 'gro kun spyi dang @048a * khyad par par 'di yi mthun rkyen sbyar ba 'brel thog de dag kun sku gsum myur du thob pa'i rgyur gyur cig dang gus ldan pa'i blo bzang ye shes kyis dam pa rnams kyi bka' 'drin gzo ba dang chos sbyin rgya chen rgya cher spel ba'i lhag bsam gyis par 'di hu re chen mor legs par bsgrubs 'di ni nyi zla ltar sa steng du khyab 'gyur cig "</col>

<col>@005b (ces zlum gtor glud dang bcas pa rnam mkha 'thor ba'am sa gtsang sar grub bzhi byang zlum po nub gru gsum lho zla gam shar phyogs su bskyal lo smras pa sprul ba'i skyes mchog dam pa rgya gar gyi 'byung bzhi gtor ma'i rten 'brel thabs mkhas kyis 'byung bzhi 'khrugs pa'i nyam thag 'gro ba la bde mdzad bdud rtsi'i char rgyun phab pa bzhin nad rims gdon bgegs mda' char mi bzad pa skyob byed rdo rje'i go cha dag dang mtshungs don bsdus spel legs snying por dril ba yi chog bsgrigs me tog gsar ba'i phreng mdzes 'di bslab gsum ldan pa'i dge slong ri khrod pas lhag bsam dag pas yang yang bskul ba'i ngor mdo rgyud man ngag 'dzin pa'i spong ba la blo bzang chos kyi rgyal mtshan zhes byas bkod sku 'bum byams pa gling du dpar du bsgrubs pa'o bkra shis 'phel par 'gyur cig</col>
</item>

<item>
<rkts></rkts>
<vol>2093</vol>
<tib>'phags pa tshe dang ye shes dpag tu med pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo</tib>
<p>1a-25b</p>
<col>@025a * ('di la 'gyur khyad phran bu yong gi 'dug na'ang 'dir rje btsun thams cad mkhyen pa t'a ra na tha'i zhal snga nas tshe dang ye shes dpag tu med pa'i mdo la t'i ka mdzad pa'i dgongs pa dang mthun pa nyid dpal dga' ldan phun tshogs gling du par du bsgrubs pa lags so 'di la brten nas bdag @025b gzhan skye dgu mtha' dag 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dpal la dbang thob par gyur cig tshe mdo'i glegs bam par du bskos tshe dang dpal nor chos bde ba tshe rabs kun tu 'phel ba'i phyir tshe ldan tshe rings bkra shis shog sarba mangga lam</col>
</item>

<item>
<rkts></rkts>
<vol>2093</vol>
<tib>po ti lnga'i smon lam</tib>
<p>1a-4a</p>
<col>@003b (zhes bka' bod rnam lnga'i smon lam 'di ni dga' ldan bshad sgrub dar rgyas gling nas blo ldan mang du thos pa'i dbu mdzad blo bzang dge 'dun gyis 'di lta bu zhig dgos zhes bskul ba'i ngor bshes gnyen mkhas pa'i drin gyis bka' bod rnam ldan @004a * cung zad sbyangs pa'i ^sprung btsun ngag dbang dpal ldan gyis sbyar ba 'dis kyang kun tu dge bar gyur cig sarba mangga lam</col>

ngo zhes lha dbang rig 'dzin rang gi gsung 'khrul med do 'dir mkha' 'gro'i snyan brgyud kyi thun mong ma yin pa'i gcod gzhung zhi pa lam zab 'di la thun mong pa'i nam mkha' sgo 'byed kyi dbang dang thun mong ma yin pa ma cig zhi ba'i dbang chog gzhan phan 'od zer thob nas gdong nas ma gtogs thun mong pa'i nam mkha' sgo 'byed thob pa tsam zhig gi gtong ba dang dbang gtan nas ma thob par gtong ba bla med kyi dbang gang rung zhig nges par thob nas de'i mjug tu thun @024b mong pa'i nam mkha' sgo 'byed mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i sgo nas tshad ldan thob pa dang rje'i rjes su thun mong ma yin pa'i nam la dge rgan bcol nas snangba gang dran tu btang na mkha' 'gro'i bka' ched yod pas 'dzems pa gal che ba yin zhes mtshungs med bla ma dam pa'i zhal nas thos so de lam zab 'di la sngon mdo smad kyi spar bcos byed rig gsung mkhan mang po dang khyad par bzhi sde smyung gnas lha khang gi mdzod pa ye shes chos 'phel nas mkha' 'gro'i snyan brgyud kyi zhi ba lam zab 'di spar gsar pa zhig rang gi mthun <item>

<tib>no title [@001a * hr'i: sngon gyi bskal ba dang po la au rgyan yul gyi nub byang mtshams dha na ko sha'i tsho gling du pad+ma ge ser sdong po la] "</tib>

<item>
<rkts></rkts>
<vol>2258</vol>
<tib>lha mi'i rnam 'dren dam pa gong sa rgyal ba'i dbang po thams cad mkhyen cing gzigs pa chen po'i mchog gi sprul pa'i sku'i rin po che'i brtan bzhugs gsol 'debs smon lam bden tshig gi mtshams sbyor dang bcas pa 'dod 'jo'i dpag bsam dbang po zhes bya ba</tib>
<p>1a-19a</p>
<col>@011b (zhes lha dang bcas pa'i 'gro ba yongs kyi mgon skyabs dpung gnyen mtshungs zla ma mchis pa gong sa rgyal ba'i dbang po thams cad mkhyen cing gzigs pa chen po'i mchog gi sprul pa'i sku rin po che'i ^ zhabs brtan gsol 'debs smon lam bden tshig gi mtshams sbyor dang bcas pa 'dod 'jo'i dpag bsam dbang po zhes bya ba 'di ni ^ @012a * gong sa lha mi'i rnam 'dren chen po gang nyid nges pa'i don du bskal ba dpag tu med pa'i snga rol nas de bzhin gshegs pa 'od zer kun nas 'phags pa dpal brtsegs rgyal po'i skur mngon par rdzogs par byang chub zin na'ang 'khor ba'i 'dam rdzab tu bying ba'i 'gro ba rnams sgrol ba'o slad du gru 'dzin ri bo'i spar dus gsum rgyal ba sras bcas kun gyi thugs rje gcig tu bsdus pa'i rang gzugs rgyal sras lag na padmo'i sku'i rnam par rol pa @012b las sku dngos kyis gdul bar mi 'os pa'i 'gro ba rnams 'dren pa'i slad du zhing khams bye ba phrag brgyar mtshan dpes spras pa'i mchog gi sprul sku nas bya dang ri dwags gsul ba'i phyir de dang de'i rnam par bstan pa'i gzo bo sprul sku'i bar gyi sprul pa'i bkod pa mtha' slas pa rim dang cig car ri rigs par ston par mdzad pa'i mtha' ni kun mkhyen nang phan tshun kho na'i spyod yul las bdag sogs 'ching ba kun ldan so so skye bo rnams kyis cha shas tsam yang brjod nus pa'i go skabs @013a * dang bral yang mi mjed 'jig rten gyi zhing 'dir sprul pa'i bkod pa ji snyed cig ston par mdzad pa las 'phags bod gnyis su ji ltar byon pa'i sprul pa'i bkod pa che long tsam zhig bka' gdams bstan pa'i chu mgo dpal aa ti sha yab sras kyi gsang chos glegs bam rin po che las ji ltar gsungs pa dang gzhan yang dam pa'i zhal las rim pa'r brgyud de kun la yongs su grags pa ni 'phags yul nor 'dzin sgeg mo'i lto bar rnam 'dren bzhi ba don kun @013b grub pa'i spyan sngar khye'u snang bar gyur ba nas bzungs chos rgyal dge ba dpal gyi bar du pandi ta grub dbang ku s'a li rgyal po 'jig rten pa las bya dang ri dwags sogs ci rigs pa'i rnam pas mkhas pa dang grub pa dpung stobs thabs mkhas sna tshogs kyi sgo nas rgyal ba'i bstan pa 'dzin skyong spel ba dang skal bar ldan pa'i sems can rnams rjes su 'dzin par mdzad bsil ldan rwa ba dkar pos khor yug tu bskor ba'i sman ljongs 'di 'phags pa nyid kyi gdul zhing du @014a * gzigs shing phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas rnams kyis bskul bas mtshams sbyar te thog mar mtsho dbri ba nas bzungs mi'i 'gro ba spel ba'i bar du gzugs sku'i bkod pa dngos su ston pa nas gang zag phal ba'i rgyud dang sa rda byin gyis rlabs pa'i bar du thugs rje'i 'jug pa cir yang ston par mdzad cing de nas rje bo'i thog ma gnya' khri btsan po nas bzungs mnga' bdag ral ba can gyi bar du sa'i tshangs pa rin dang cig car ci rigs pa'i @014b rnam par bstan nas mnga' 'bangs bde bar skyong ba dang dam pa'i chos kyi dbu brnyengs shing srol btod dar rgyas su mdzad pa dge ba bcu'i khrims bcas shing chab 'bangs thams cad chos 'byor bde skyid dpal la sbyor bar mdzad de rjes 'brom ston rgyal ba'i 'byung gnas nas pan chen pad+ma badzra gyi bar du dge bsnyen dang rig sngags 'chang ba'i dbang po mkhas grub gnyis ldan rim dang cig car rigs pa'i tshul bzungs nas bod yul mun @015a * nag gi gling rum du rgyal bstan gsal ba'i sgron me rgya cher spor par mdzad cing thams cad mkhyen pa dge 'dun grub pa dpal bzang po nas bzungs bde chen chos kyi rgyal po yon tan rgya mtsho'i bar du gser sbyangs cod pan 'dzin pa'i ngur smrig 'chang ba bar ma chad pa'i tshul du byon nas thub bstan rgya mtsho'i yang snying rgyal ba gnyis pa'i ring lugs kyi rgyal mtshan srid gsum rtse mo'i bar du mthon por sgreng bar mdzad khyad par @015b rigs dang dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i khyab bdag nges pa don gyi thams cad mkhyen pa chen po ngag dbang blo bzang rgya mtsho'i sku'i rnam par bstan nas bcu phrag rig pa'i gzhung lugs dang mdo rgyud spyi bye brag gi tshig don mtha' dag phyogs re tsam ma yin par thub pa'i bstan pa lus yongs su rdzogs pa thos bsam sgom gsum gyis gtan la 'bebs par mdzad pas rgyal ba bu ram shing ba'i ring lugs rtsod pa'i dus 'dir ches cher gsal bar gyur @016a * cing dpal lag na rdo rje'i sprul pa mi'i dbang po bstan 'dzin chos kyi rgyal pos gangs ljongs kyi 'gro ba ma rungs pa'i rgyal phran bsul bus gtses shing nyam thag pa rnams dbugs phyungs shing rang dbang du byas nas ^ gong sa lha mi'i rnam 'dren chen po'i zhabs 'og tu tshud pa'i skal bzang la byor bar mdzad pa brtse chen byams pa'i thugs kyis bdag gir bzhes nas dge ba bcu'i khrims lugs kyi srol nyams pa rnams sor chud par mdzad de chos @016b srid lugs gnyis kyi nyi zla'i snang bas 'jig rten dkar por bsgyur bar mdzad la de rjes su'ang thams cad mkhyen pa blo bzang rin chen tshangs dbyangs rgya mtsho nas bzungs lha mi'i rnam 'dren chen po ngag dbang blo bzang bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan 'phrin las rgya mtsho dpal bzang po'i bar du gser sbyangs cod pan mdzes pa'i sdom brtson rgyal po'i tshul 'dzin pa 'ba' zhig gi rnam par rim par byon nas 'gro ba ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral pa dang ma grol ba @017a * rnams grol ba dang dbugs ma byin pa rnams dbugs dbyung bar mdzad pa'i rnam par thar pa bsam brjod kyi yul las 'das shing dus kyi mtha' 'dir yang rang nyid kyi gdul zhing byang phyogs bho ta'i rgyal khams kyi 'gro ba dbu rgong pa ma rungs pa gdul dka' ba rnams brtse chen byams pa'i thugs kyis ma bor bar slar yang skye ba sprul sku'i zla tshes kyi rang zhal gsar du dngom pa mchog gi sprul pa'i sku rin po che nying ring por ma thogs @017b par tshul bstan thos psam sgom gsum gyi mdzad pa mtha' dag dka' ba med par mthar phyin nas gsum ldan sdom brtson rgyal po'i tshul gyis thub bstan yongs rdzogs kyi bdag por bzhengs rgyu'i thog ma'i rten 'brel gyi 'jug sgo dam pa mthon mthing gi lan bu dor nas mtshan snyan gsar ba'i dbyar rnga skal bzang mdongs mtha' dga' ba'i gsos su sgrog pa dang lhan cig zhabs zung mi 'gyur rdo rje'i khri 'phang mthon por bskal @018a * pa bye bar brtan par bzhugs nas gsan bas ma sgom gsum sogs chos dang srid ki bzhed don mtha' dag gegs med bde blag tu 'grub pa'i smon lam bden tshig gi mtshams sbyor ris su ma chad pa'i 'dus sde rnams kyi zhal 'don dang dad ldan ser skya mchog dman mtha' dag gis ngag 'don du byas chog pa 'di lta bu'i zhig dgos zhes bur rgyal chol kha gsum gyi 'dzin mar chos srid gser gyi khor los dbang bsgyur @018b zhing gong sa lha mi'i rnam 'dren chen po'i lugs zung gi 'phrin las kyi gtugs dkar dgung du 'degs pa la gzhan dring mi 'jog pa'i rnam dpyod can rgyal tshab thung zhan rje drung ho thog thu chen pos srid du ring ba'i lha rdzas kyis thog drangs bdog pa'i gnang ba skyes gya nom pa dang bcas nan tan chen pos bskul ma mdzad pa drang du blangs te rgyal rigs kyi bandhes nor gling bskal bzang pho brang du 'bru mang zhes sa stag gnam lo'i dka' @019a * thub zla ba'i dkar phyogs kyi bzang po gnyis pa de gza' gos sngon can rgyu skar tha skar sbyor bas rlung sbyor chen gzhon dbyangs ai nyi ma sprel 'char ba'i gza' skar 'phrod sbyor phun sum tshogs pa'i phyed yol snga cha'i bdud rtsi thun mtshams kyi thog tu grub par sbyar nas gsol ba shugs drag tu btab pa'o sarba mangga lam dge legs 'phel</col>

<col>@009b (ces phyag rgya chen po'i ngo sprod tshul gyis 'di yang 'di nang gi chos brgyad smon pa'i zlog gar ltar mthong nas @010a * dben pa'i ri sul du drang srong gi spyod tshul gyis 'dug nas lam 'di la nyams len snying por byed pa gnas bcu rab 'byams pa dge 'dun rgya mtshon dang ha mthong dka' bcu pa shes rab seng ge gnyis kyis snga mo nas yang yang bskul zhing gzhan yang nges don phyag chen gyi nyams len byed par rang gi  slob ma mang pos bskul ba dang khyad par rje grub pa'i dbang phyug thams cad mkhyen pa rgyal ba dben sa pa chen po de nyid kyis rang gzhan la 'doms par mdzad pa'i nyams mgur zhig @010b tu bshes gnyen bsten tshul nas zhi lhag gi bar bka' gdams lam rim ltar gdams nas mjug tu bshad ma mthag pa'i lam 'di ma yin pa da lta'i gangs can pa lam grags pa'i phyag rgya chen po'i gdams dag mthar thug pa da lha yi ger 'god par mi nus so zhes de dus dgag bya'i dbang gis mi 'god pa phyi dus la dgongs pa dper na dam chos bdar dkar du sangs rgyas ye shes rab tu rtogs bya'i phyir thabs 'di rang byung gis ni mdzd gyur gyi de dag rnams la khyed cag sangs rgyas su @011a * 'gyur ro zhes ni nas yang mi gsung ngo ce phyir zhe ni skyob pa dus la gzigs zhes gsungs pa dang 'dra ba'i bzhed pa bsgrub pa'i phyir ston pa mnyam med sh'akya'i rgyal po nas bzung ste bdag gi rtsa ba'i bla ma thams cad mkhyen cing gzigs pa sangs rgyas ye shes zhabs kyi zhal snga nas kyi bar lam 'di mngon sum du thugs nyams su bstar pa'i byin rlabs kyi brgyud ma mnyam shing dam tshig la sel ba ma zhugs pa'i rigs u byung zhing mdo rgyud dam pa'i man ngag 'dzin pa'i spong ba pa blo bzang chos kyi rgyal mtshan gyis dge ldan rnam par rgyal ba'i gling du sbyar ba'o</col>

<col>@009a * (bla blu'i cho ga rin chen srog gi chad 'thud zhes bya ba 'di bla 'gugs dgos pa 'ga' zhig gi skabs lag tu bza' btung gi rigs zhig thogs te ming nas khyi 'bod pa bzhin byed pa las bya thabs gzhan mi shes pa mang po mthong bas rkyen byas te mdos gto glud kyi cho ga 'di rigs sde snod la sbyangs pa'i dge bshes rnams 'gal rkyen med cing lto 'grangs nyi mas dros pa'i skabs spangs bya dang nad gdon sogs kyis bcos dus blang byar mdzad pas spangs blang gang gi phyogs yin ma shes kyang rma khar phan na khyi tshil gyi dpe bzhin nye bar mkho ba'i skabs kyang srid stams te btsun gzugs dharma badzra gyis yid dga' chos 'phel zhes bya ba'i skyed mos tshal du bris so mangga lam</col>
</item>

<item>

<item>
<rkts></rkts>
<vol>2405</vol>
<tib>dpal rdo rje nag po chen po gur gyi mgon po lha bcu gnyis ma'i sgrub mchod gtor bsngo bzlas bshags bskang bstod gsol kha bskul bzlog mnga' gsol dang bcas pa phyogs gcig tu bsgrigs pa bstan bsrung dbang po mnyes byed mchod sprin 'dod don myur bsgrub zhes bya ba lung 'di'i dbang rjes gnang lung ma thob pa dang dad pa dang dam tshig dang mi ldan pa rnams la mtshan dang dpe cha tsham yang mi bstan par shin tu gsang zhing swa ba'i bka' rgya can</tib>
<p>1a-119a</p>
<col>@087a * (ces dpal rdo rje nag po chen po gur gyi mgon po lha bcu gnyis ma'i sgrub mchod gtor bsngo bzlas bshags bskang bstod gsol kha bskul bzlog mnga' gsol dang bcas pa phyogs gcig tu bsgrigs pa bstan bsrung dbang po mnyes byed mchod sprin 'dod don myur sgrub zhes bya ba 'di yang sngon khal kha'i yul phyogs 'dir bstan pa ma dar pa'i dus su ching gir rgyal po'i rigs brgyud du bsam bzhin sku 'khrungs @087a * pa'i mthu stobs dbang phyug aa pa tha'i mtshan can dpon chen pos ^ rgyal dbang gsum pa bsod nams rgya mtsho'i zhal ma 'jal ba la de nyid phyag na rdo rje rnam 'phrul rdo rje rgyal po phag mo grub pa'i skye mthar ngos 'dzin gnang la dpal rdo rje rgyal po'i mtshan cas tha ma ka dang sh'akya thub sku brten mes mi thub dang phag gru'i thang ka sogs rten khyad par can rnams stsal nas yul 'dir bstan pa dar pa'i rten 'brel du sngon gyi mong gol rgyal po rnams kyi srol bzhin sa lugs 'dzin pa'i bla ma zhig gnang ba la mchod nas lha khang rten bcas dang rten gras su 'gro mgon rgyal 'phags pa dang gur mgon lcam dral bzhengs dgos tshul sogs zhal bkod mdzad bzhin grub pa byin brlabs che ba aer te ni jo bor grags pa'i gtsug lag khang 'di'i bla mar rgyal ba nyid kyi tshab du spyan drangs pa'i grub thob bka' bcu bya ba la rgyal pos she re ke thu pandi ta gu sh'ri chos rje zhes mtshan gsol ba de nyid nas bzung ste mkhas grub bar ma chad par rim bzhin byon nas byin brlabs pa'i gdan sar ^ skyabs mgon rje dam pa dang rdo rje rgyal po'i bka' lung gis bsgos te khyi la sengge'i ming btags pa ltar bla ma nom chis chos rjer 'bod pa kho bo cag gis dgon pa 'dir sngar nas rgyun gyi phyag len la sa lugs kyi gur mgon 'don bzhin yod kyang yi dam chos bsrung 'di rnams kyi dbang sogs kyi rgyun ma thob pa dang 'don cha'i dpe @087b yang khungs gtsang zhing yi ge dag pa phyag len gsal po sogs mi 'dug pas de lta bu zhig thob na bstan pa'i rgyun yun du gnas pa la phan par bsam te bstan pa'i mnga' bdag lcang skya rol pa'i rdo rje 'chang gi sku gzhogs la sngar gyi rgyu mtshan rnams zhus pa la de ltar byas na spyir bzang ba yin kyang gzhan nas rnyed thabs mi 'dug pas grub na khyod rang dang ma grub kyang rang gi slob dpon lta bu zhig sa skyar mdags ste de'i bdag chen gyi drung nas dbang bskur sogs yongs rdzogs mnos na shin tu legs ces bka' phebs pa rnams thu she ye thu han tshe brtan rdo rje nyid la zhus par de bzhin gnang ste skyabs mgon dam pa'i dgongs rdzogs kyi rnam dkar 'bul ba po mi sna rnams dang stabs gcig tu nged gzhon nu'i dus nas bla mar bsten dge bskos chen mo dge slong blo bzang chos grub bya ba rgyal po'i mi sna mngags pa de me sprel lor dbus gtsang du phyin la rgyal ba yab sras dang sprul pa'i chos skyong rnams la lung bstan zhus pa la legs so'i gnang ba stsal ba ltar 'chi med khon sa skya pa ste mtshan mchog gsum ldan gyi gdung rabs rnams kyi gdan sa chen po dpal ldan sa skyar phyin nas ^ snyigs ma'i dus dir grub chen birwa pa'i sku gsung thugs dang dbyer pa'i rnam par rol pas bstan 'gro'i dpal du gyur ba bla mas skya pa chen po ngag dbang kun dga' blo gros sangs rgyas bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po'i zhabs kyi padmo'i drung du dad stobs kyi @088a * dbang phyug rdo rje thu she ye thu rgyal pos 'bul ba'i yi ge rten bcas phul ba la ^ sku gzhogs rin po che nyid kyis thugs shin tu dgyes bzhin pa nas bla brang go bzhi las bzhi thog bla brang gi nang bla ma dang yi dam mkha' 'gro chos skyong gi rten khyad par can rnams kyi drung du sa skya pandi ta kun dga' rgyal mtshan gyis mdzad pa'i thub pa dgongs gsal gyi ljags lung nas brtsams ste gur mgon lha bcu gnyis ma'i rdul mtshon gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba dang de'i sgrub dkyil dang gzhan dbang bskur tshul dang bcas pa shin tu gsal po thugs rtsom brtses gzigs stsal pa dang sku gzhogs nas yongs 'dzin rje drung rin po che byams pa rin chen rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po'i drung du khal kha'i rgyal po'i mi sna 'di la nged kyis bskur dgos pa rnams skur zin pas khyod nyid kyis rdor man ngag lugs kyi phyi nang gi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba dang gur mgon lha brgyad ma dang gur gyi mgon po khro 'cu'i bsrung 'khor rdo rje brag rdzongs ma'i rjess gnang sogs rjes gnang gtso gal che ba rnams dang mgon po   me 'bar ma sogs kyi lung mang po dang gur mgon lha bcu gnyis ma'i dkyil 'khor sgrub mchod bya tshul dang bskang ba'i phyag len gyi 'khrid rnams zhib par bskur dgos tshul gyi bka' phebs bzhin gang des de rnams yongs rdzogs gnang ba'o gzhan yang bzhi thog bla brang nas snga phyir rim bzhin gnang rten @088a * yab rje rdo rje 'chang gis sa chen gong ma'i sku brnyan dang chos rje khu dpon rin po che'i rnam kar thang ka mal lo ts'a ba'i nang rten rdo mgon yid bzhin nor bu gur mgon lha bcu gnyis ma'i dkyil thang rab gnas can sogs yi dam chos skyong rnams kyi sku brnyan mang po dang gong ma lnga'i bka' 'bum yongs rdzogs gur mgon chos 'byung sogs dang de sras sa skya pa ae wam bzang po nas mgon bod me 'bar ma dang yab rje rdo rje 'chang gi gdung thal sa tstsha sogs dang yang sa skya pa dbang bsdud snying po nas li ma spyan ras gzigs dang dam rdzas las grub pa'i kyee rdor gur mgon sogs kyi sku brnyan dang gsung ngag rin po che'i khog bug sogs glegs bam du ma dang rang gi phyag rdzas rdor dril t'a ma ru 'phreng ba sogs byin rten mang po gangga'i rgyun ltar stsal gzhin pa'i ngos nas brtse bas bskyangs ba bka' drin shin tu che che gyur ba yin lags de lta bu yon mchod rnams kyi bka' drin bsam pa dang rang re'i dgon 'di la sngar gyi srol rgyun ltar 'di nyid nyin re bzhin 'don pa la lag tu blang ba bde ba dang cha lag tshang ba 'byung khungs dang bcas pa zhig bstan pa ji srid gnas kyi bar du bzhugs par bya ba'i lhag bsam rnam dag gi nye bar bskul te sa chen nyid kyis ched du mdzad pa'i gur mgon lha bcu gnyis ma'i sgrub dkyil mgon po rnam rol gsal ba'i nor bu la gzhi byas la dam pa kun dga' grags kyi mdzad pa'i 'di'i bskang bshags chen @089a * mo nag po mchod rten sgrub pa sa skya lo tsa'i bskang gsar dang gtor bsngo chen mo gzhan yang sa lugs 'di ka'i brgyud 'dzin dam pa mang po'i yig cha las byung dang khyad par zhal ngo nang brgyud kyi zhal shes man ngag dang mthong brgyud phyag len gyis brgyan cing rgyas par bklags chog tu bsgrigs te bka' drin mtshungs med khyab bdag rdo rje 'chang chen su ma ti dharma siddhi shri bha dra'i zhabs rdung nas gur mgon 'di'i dbang rjes gnang lung man ngag zab mo rnams legs par thob cing bsnyen pa tshad du 'khyol bas mtshan ma cung zad thob par rlob pa dge slong grags pa dar rgyas sam ming gzhan rig pa 'dzin pa shr'i ha sa badzra n'a tha ming can gyis me pho 'brug lo'i rgyal zla' ba'i mar ngo'i tshes bcu mkha' 'gro 'du ba'i dus bzang khyad par can la rgyal ba sras dang bcas pas byin gyis brlabs shing de dag gi sku gsung thugs kyi rten mang du bzhugs pa lung rtogs kyi bstan pa rin po che'i 'byung gnas lhun grub bde chen rin chen jo bo'i gtsug lag khang gi nye 'dab gur mgon lha khang la pan chen rin po che'i bkas dge 'dun don grub gling gi mtshan thogs par bla ma dang mkha' 'gro chos skyong khyad par can rnams la gsol ba rtse gcig tu 'debs bzhin pa'i ngang nas legs par sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni pi lig thu rol dpon dbu mdzad blo bzang tshe ring gis bgyis pa'o 'dis kyang spyi sgos kyi bstan pa rin @090a * par bya rigs so</col>

<item>

cis kyang dgos zhes rten 'di bzhengs mchod sogs la lhag bsam rnam par dag pas yid drangs te sgo du ma nas 'bad rtsol dang spro shugs kyis dor ma tshul mthun sgrub pa dang brtson snying stobs phul du bslangs te bde ldan gling dang tshe 'phel gling sogs rang gzhan gyi yul phyogs mang po'i chos sde rnams su yang rje bla ma'i dus mchod sogs la cho ga 'di lta bu gtod srol 'byung na shin tu legs par <tib>zhugs pa dang gnas pa'i 'phags pa'i dge 'dun gyi rnam gzhag gi mtha' dpyod skal bzang 'jug ngogs</tib>
<p>1a-136a</p>
<col>@134a * (ces zhugs pa dang gnas pa'i 'phags pa'i dge 'dun gyi rnam gzhag gi mtha' dpyod skal ldan 'jug ngogs 'di ni rang gi slob bu rab 'byams @0134b pa blo bzang tshul khrims kyis lha rdzas dang sbub cha rtsi dmar bcas bskul zhing nye lam rang gi grwa ba mtho dman mang pos kyang dgos zhes yang yang bskul ba dang khyad par grwa tshangs kyi skabs dang po'i 'dzin grwa'i skyor dpon bkra shis don 'grub rab 'byams pa kun dga' bkra shis chos mdzad dge legs rgya mtsho dge slong blo bzang bsam 'phel sogs grwa pa kun gyis kha dar sum 'brel dri ma med pa byur dkar gyi 'phreng ba rgyan can ras dkar yug zung dang bcas bskul ba dang du blangs te sngon nas 'di skor la ring du 'dris par byas te zhib tu dri gtug gi legs par gtan la phab nas ma rtog pa dang log par rtog pa dang the tshom gyi dri ma med par nges pa skyes pa theg pa chen po'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen zla med pa nges pa don gyi thams cad mkhyen pa chos kyi rje 'jam dbyangs bzhad pa'i rdo rje'i zhal snga nas kyi zhabs rdul spyi bor len pa sh'akya'i dge slong sdom pa gsum gyi bcas pa la mig 'bras ltar gces spras kyis bsrung zhing mdo sngags kyi gzhung lugs la sbyangs pa mi dman pa dka' bcu smra ba ngag dbang bkra shis pa'i dpal gyis 'di skor gyi rang gzhan gyi yig cha phal cher dang mngon pa gnyis rtsa 'grel la legs par dpyad nas @135a * rje rin po che'i legs bshad gser phreng gzhir bzhag nas dge 'dun nyi shu chen mo dang rnam bshad snying po rgyan gnyis kyis kha bskang nas skyes bdag gi lo hor zla gnyis pa'i grwa la tshes la dge ldan bshad sgrub dar rgyas bkra shis 'khyil ba'i gling nas sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni rab 'byams pa kun dga' bkra shis dang dge slong blo bzang bsam 'phel gnyis kyis bris pa 'dis kyang rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che sgo thams cad nas dar zhing rgyas la yun ring du gnas par gyur cig  ` 'dod don gang sgrub kyang de la sgrib sdig sbyang ba gal che bas bsags sbyangs kyi gnad 'ga' zhig ni rim gro gang byed kyang yon mchod gnyis kas ched du bya ba sems can ji snyed yod pa'i don du dgos pas srog bslu zhing skyob par re ba nad las 'grol ba'i ched du dge sgrub tu khas blangs pa bzhin du 'phongs pa de las sgrol ma grol gang yang rung tshe yi phreng ba gang du'ang ma rgan ji snyed yod pa rnams dge ba bcu dang bden bzhi nas rnam mkhyen gyi bar 'god pa bstan 'gro'i @135b don rgya cher bsgrub ste rdo rje 'chang gi go 'phang 'thob pa bsngo na gnad du 'gro ba'i gdams ngag yin pas nad pa dang sman rtsis pa sogs phan 'dogs pa'i las byed pa'i rim gro pa rnams la brda sprad pa dang rang la 'brel ba gsum ci rigs kyis 'brel thogs pa'i tshe las 'das pa rnams dang sgos dpar 'di bsgrub pa chos sbyin rgya cher spel bar byed pa bstan pa'i sbyin bdag mchog gsum 'phrin las kyi gzi 'od 'bar bar byed pa'i zhabs gtegs pa ha ka lag che blo'u 'dzangs kyis rgyu sbyor te bi shwa karma gnyis pa dge slong 'jam dpal gyis brko bas mtshon 'khor ba thog med nas drin gzhal du med pa yod do cog gis theg chen gyi phyir mi ldog pa'i dge 'dun dkon mchog dang dus nam kun tu lta spyod mthun te srid zhi'i rgud pa mtha' dag las grol ba'i mthar thug gi mngon mtho phun sum tshogs pa'i bde ba bsgrub pa dang de bzhin du gzhan la'ang byed du 'jug par bskul ba'i don dang rang gis kyang tshe ring nad med mthar phyin pa'i rten 'brel du dmigs te 'bangs rnams @136a * tshul bzhin skyong ba sa 'eeng no yon gyi aa 'ee dmag dman rnams dge bcu'i lam la 'god pa d'a la'i t'a 'ee chen gung gi dgon par ^ gnam bsgos rgyal pos bde skyong gling du bsngags pa gtsug lag khang gi nye 'dabs su rab byung bco lnga'i bgrang gnyis par sku gsum phun tshogs gling du bkod pa'i tshul tshe spel dbang phyug rdo rjes bris pa'o</col>

<col>@031b (ces 'phags pa thugs rje chen po zhal bcu gcig pa grub dbang dpal mo'i lugs kyi sgrub thabs smyung bar gnas pa'i cho ga bya tshul dang bcas pa phan bde'i snang ba gsar @032a * dngos zhes bya ba 'di ni bstan pa'i gsal byed dza ya pandi ta hu thog thu dang lha ldan spro bde khang gsar ba'i dkar po'i phyogs brgyad pa spyi tshogs dang 'bras spungs sgo mang aor du su pe'i se rnam rgyal rdo rje'i shog dka' bcu klu sgrub rgya mtsho bde yangs rab 'byams pa blo bzang nor bu sogs nas bskul ma rim par byung bar brten rtsol 'dun thog nyer ra khal kha nas dad stobs dang ldan pa khe pe'i aam pan pe'i se tshe chog skyabs kyis bskul ma byung bar rten dpal mgon 'phags pa klu sgrub dang grub bsnyes dpal mos mdzad pa'i rgya gzhung sogs la gzhugs gtso cher phyag na padmo'i thams cad mkhyen pa dge 'dun rgya mtshos mdzad pa'i sgrub thabs 'jug pa bde bar brten dar po che bar 'dug pas de nyid gzhir bzung mkhas grub tshad ldan gzhan gyis mdzad pa'i cho ga dang dam pa'i phyag bzhes sogs nas kha 'geng 'os kyis legs par brgyan te ^sh'akya'i dge slong chos smra ba blo bzang skal bzang rgya mtshos 'phags pa 'jig rten dbang phyug gi pho brang po ta la'i gzims chung nyi 'od 'khyil bar sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni dar khan dge slong skal bzang yon tan gyis bgyis pa'o</col>
</item>

<item>
<rkts></rkts>
<vol>2557</vol>
<tib>no title [@001a * na mo manydzu shr'i ye (skyabs sems sngon du btang) sw'a bha wa(s stong par sbyangs) stong pa'i ngang las pad zla'i steng du dhi: yig mthing nag de las 'od zer 'phros don gnyis byas]"</tib>
<p>1a-1b</p>

<col>@007b (ces byang phyogs bstan 'gro'i dpal mgon ^rje btsun dam pa rin po che ngag dbang blo bzang chos kyi nyi ma bstan 'dzin dbang phyug dpal bzang po'i zhal snga nas kyi gsang gsum rnam thar rgya mtsho lta bu las chu thig tsam zhig rjes su dran pa'i sgo nas bstod cing gsol ba btab pa'i tshigs su bcad pa skal bzang dad pa'i sgo 'byed ces bya ba 'di ni snga mo nas dge bshes dharma tsakras dngul tam lha dar bcas bskul ba dang nyi char chos kyi spun zla 'ga' yis kyang rab dkar lha rdzas bcas bskul zhing rang nyid kyis kyang dad pas mtshams sbyar te sa mtha'i btsun chung gyi na pa ^mgon de'i bka' lung gis nom chi pi lig thu aerti ni mer ken she dar chos rjer bsngags pa sngags ram pa blo bzang chos 'dzin gyis sug bris su bgyis pa dge legs 'phel 'dis kyang 'gro kun bshes gnyen dam pa'i mgoon gyis mi 'bral bar dgyes bzhin rjes su 'dzin pa'i rgyur gyur cig dge'o ` swasti rgyal kun mkhyen rab dbang @008a * po 'jam pa'i dbyangs mthon mthing zur phud bregs te ngur smrig gi gar rol rje btsun chos kyi nyi ma yi zhabs pad lan brgyar dran pas phyag bgyi'o gang de'i gsang gsum mdzad pa'i rnam par thar rab gsal gsol 'debs gser gyi a'a darsha dad ldan gsol dpon bkra shis nyi ma yis chos sbyin 'dzad med dpar gyi sgo 'phar phye dge 'dis 'gro kun dam pa'i mgon gyis bzung khyad par mgon khyod rigs ldan drag por bzhengs rdzogs ldan bstan pa'i 'od snang 'bar ba'i tshe gsung gi bdud rtsis smin cing grol bar shog  dge legs 'phel</col>

<col>@010ab (ces rnga mong ga-yang 'gugs dgos 'dod 'byung zhes bya ba 'di ni da lta snyigs ma'i dus su rnam par dkar ba'i bsod nams bsags pa'i gang zag nyen kyi skar ma bzhin 'ga' zhig yod kyang phyugs bzhi longs spyod yod na'ang stong stod pa tshad med pa zhes pa'i dbang gis rkyen gyis ma byas kyang mang bas nor gyi lha rnams la gang 'dod pa'i 'don grub zhu ba ga-yang 'gugs kyi rim pa dam pa gong ma rnams kyis mdzad pa mang du yod kyang byung ba'i gsung yin pa'i de la thab lha bskyed dang mchod pa bsangs ga-yang 'gugs sogs kyi la bskangs te mthun mong ma yin pa'i dngos grub 'dod pa can rnams la dgos med na'ang 'jig pa'i dngos grub 'dod pa bdag 'dra ba res 'ga' la phan snyan dkar ba'i sems kyis bskul te dge slong gzugs 'dzin aartha siddhi'i ming can gyis sug bris su sbyar ba dge legs 'phel bkra shis par gyur cig dge'o legs so</col>

<col>@003a * (lha klu gzhi bdag sogs la ja mchod 'bul ba'i cho ga bde legs kun 'byung zhes bya ba 'di ni bakshida wa aindra radna sa snyigs ma'i dus lnga brgya tha ma'i dus 'dir tha @003b mal skye bo phal cher ma rig dbang gis spyod pa mi mkhas pas sa gnyan brgo rdo gnyan rlog shing gnyan gcad chu klung ne'u klog brag thag gnyan prang prang pa pa dang mi gtsang thab zhob sogs byas pa'i rkyen gyis lha klu gzhi bdag btsan 'byung sa bdag sogs kyi sems khros zhing 'khrugs pas chur chu dus su ma 'brebs pa dang than pa sad ser char drag thog glug rlung dmar mi nad god kha 'byung ba dang gcan gzan 'phar spyang bya khyi rku phrog chom rkun sogs nye bar 'tshe ba'i ltas ngan mtshan ma gyur ba la de dag zhi bar byed pa'i thabs su 'gyur ma skam pa'i bsams pas kun nas blangs te sh'akya'i dge slong grags pa bshad sgrub kyis mdzad lha mchog rnams dga' bar byed pa'i bsangs mchod bcu gsum mu tig 'phreng ba la rigs 'gre byas te sug bris su gyes pa'i lha klu gzhi bdag sa bdag btsan 'byung sogs la @004a * thub na nyin re bzhin ja mchod 'bul na shin tu legs mi thub na dus su 'bul na'am de rnams dga' zhing 'bral med rtag tu grogs mdzad pas dgos pa thams cad ltun gyis sgrub tshe bsod dpal 'byor snyan grags nor phyugs sogs rab tu 'phel nag phyogs gdon bgegs gcan gzan 'phar spyang bya khyi rku 'phrog chom rkun sogs nyer 'tshe mtha' dag zhi zhing mthun rkyen bsam don yid bzhin du 'grub pa sogs gnas skabs mthar thug gi phan yon mtha' yas 'byung ngo 'dis kyang sems can thams cad phan thogs par gyur cig</col>

<vol>2697</vol>
<tib>lam rim ni "</tib>
<p>3a-43a inc [*missing page from 1a-2b 4a-13b*]"</p>
<col>@042b (ces rgyal ba'i gsung rab rab 'byams thams cad kyi gnad don yongs su rdzogs pa gcig tu bsdus pa byang chub lam gyi rim pa'i gdams pa zab mo nyams su len tshul gyi man ngag thun mong ma yin pa phan bde'i lam bzang zhes bya ba 'di ni rang gi rgyun gyi nyams len dang blo dman gzhan dag la'ang phan 'dod kyi bsam pas kun nas bslangs te pan chen thams cad @043a * mkhyen pa chen po'i rdo rje'i gsung byang chub bde lam nyid gzhir bzung ste de'i don gyi snying po rnams mtshang ba med par bsdus pa la gal che ba'i dmigs skor 'ga' zhig gis kyang kha bskangs las dang po pas tshig gi sgo nas kyang bshar sbyang byed pa la brjod pa bde ched dngos gzhi'i 'khrid dmigs rnams kyang ngag 'don gyi tshul du bsgrigs rang gi bla ma dam pa'i man ngag phyag bzhes kyis kyang legs par brgyan nas 'jug pa shin tu bde bar bla ma dam pa du ma'i bka' drin gyis nye bar 'tsho ba'i btsun gzugs snyom las pa ^dam tshig rdo rjes gangs can bod kyi rdo rje gdan chen po lha ldan sprul pa'i gtsug lag khang gi nye 'dabs zhig tu nye bar sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni chos mthun snying gi slob bu dge slong blo bzang nam mkha' rdo rjes bgyis pa'o 'dis kyang 'jam mgon rgyal ba'i mdo sngags kyi bstan pa rin po che 'di nyid nam yang mi nub cing phyogs dus gnas skabs thams cad du dar zhing rgyas la yun ring du gnas pa dang bstan 'dzin gyi skyes chen dam pa thams cad sku khams bzang zhing sku tshe ring ba dang rnam par dkar ba'i mdzad pa 'phrin las dar rgyas su 'byung ba dang 'gro ba kun kyang rgyal ba dgyes pa'i lam mchog 'di dag dang nam yang mi 'bral zhing zung 'jug rdo rje 'chang chen po'i go 'phang myur du thob pa'i rgyur gyur cig 'di'i mthus bdag kyang tshe rabs thams cad du theg mchog mgon gyis rjes bzung la ma bzang 'di thos bsam bsgom dang 'chad rtsong rtsom pa yis 'dzin skyong spel la mnga' dbang 'byor bar shog  dge legs 'phel</col>
</item>

<item>
<rkts></rkts>

<item>

<p>1a-11b</p>
<col>@011a * (zhes bla ma'i rnal 'byor dang 'brel bar byang chub lam rim gyi snying po'i don nyams su len @011b tshul legs gsung kun gyi sgo 'byed skal ldan re skong zhes bya ba 'di ni rang gi slob ma don gnyer can 'ga' zhig gis lam rim gyi gnad don tshang ba'i nyams len 'khyer bde ba zhig dgos zhes nan tan du bskul ngor tshul 'di nyid byin rlabs khyad par du 'phags shing 'jug pa bde bar mthong nas bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' drin kho nas 'tsho ba'i btsun gzugs snyom las pa ^dam tshig rdo rjes bla ma'i gsung rgyud las byung ba'i man ngag ji lta ba bzhin bris pa 'dis kyang 'jam mgon rgyal ba'i mdo sngags kyi bstan pa rin po che 'di dag nam lang mi nub cing phyogs dus kun tu dar zhing rgyas la yun ring du gnas par gyur cig dge legs 'phel</col>
</item>

<item>

<col>@018a * (ces rta mgrin gsang sgrub kyi sgo nas sri mnan byed tshul rdo rje'i lhun po brtsegs pa zhes bya ba 'di yang dus kyi dbang gi sri'i gnod pa shin tu che bar 'dug pas mnan thabs kyi yi ge lag tu blang bde ba zhig ces kyang brtsom shig ces don gnyer ba du mas snga phyir yang yang bskul ba la brten nas rang phyogs kyi bla ma gong mas mdzad pa'i yig cha'i rigs ma mthong shing mi bskyod rdo rjes byas zer ba zhig 'dug pa lha mo'i sgrub sri lte phur nag mo dang dam sri gnyis kha sbyor du gnon pa sogs sri'i ngo bo tsam yang ngos ma zin pa'i lag len tha chad dang lcags mkhar gyi 'don cha la gro sngags pa'i dpe 'khyams kyi tshog 'ga' zhig bsres te sengge'i ya mgal dang phag gi ma mgal mi 'grigs bzhin du sbyar ba'i yig nyog la ming rdo rje'i thog @018b mda' zhes 'dogs pa ngo tsha bor ba'i brdul zhugs su snang la sngags pa ral khur ngoms pa mang pos kyang thod rabs tsam la brten nas snang bar gang shar byed pa las lag len tshad ldan byed mkhan dkon par 'dug pas gsal zhing 'gril la lag tu glang chog ma 'di 'dra zhig bgyis na rma khar phan na khyi tshil gyi dpe bzhin mchog dam mang po la nye bar mkho ba'i skabs kyang srid snyam te btsun gzugs ^dharma badzra gyis rtsa ba'i gzhung 'byung ba rin chen kun 'dus dang sgo bstun yig cha dum nas kha 'geng 'os kyis brgyan te 'phar ba zhes pa lcags mo glang gi lo'i cho 'phrul zla ba'i yar ngo'i tshes brgyad kyi nyin zla brang bkra shis 'od 'bar du thun gcig la rdzogs par sbyar ba'o ) "</col>

<tib>rnam rgyal khro rgyal mgon po kha mchu nag po gsang ba'i bzlog bsgyur</tib>
<p>1a-14a</p>
<col>@012b (ces pa 'di ni sgrub chen thab mkhas @013a * mchos dbyings dbang phyug rdo rje mdzad pa'o phan yon ni lhog gzer mdze phog mig pas ltags me dpal lan chags mi'i nad phyugs nad dang mi yi tshogs rnams la 'brum dkar 'brum ser 'brum nag be bge la sogs pa'i nad thams cad rab tu zhi bar byed par 'gyur ro nad gdon dgra bgegs thams cad las bsrung bar 'gyur ro 'srog lus dbang thang rlung rta sme ba dgu sbar kha brgyad lo bskor bcu gnyis la sogs pa'i 'gal rkyen bar chad zhi bar 'gyur ro bod sngags ngan pa khyad kha phur kha dang rgya nad byad kha nad phur kha gtang kha dmod kha dang mi'i kha mchu 'jigs pa las 'grol par 'gyur ro mi nad dang phyugs nad la god kha mi phyugs kyi dus min 'chi ba dang ngan sri dang byis pa'i gdon chen bcwo lnga'i 'jigs pa thams cad las thar bar 'gyur ro bkra mi shis pa skyes bo rtsod pa rgyal po chad pa lo skeg zla skeg nyin @013b skeg zhag skeg dus skeg dang pha khu'i dang nyi du'i 'byung 'dre thams cad kyi sil bar 'gyur ro lha dang klu dang srin po dang sde brgyad dang dgra dang ro langs dang yi dwags dang sha za dang ma mo dang khrag zor gyis 'jigs pa thams cad las bzlog par 'gyur ro bkra shis skoms dang dug mu ge dang rdzun tshig kha smras thams cad las bzlog par 'gyur ro sa bdag klu gnyen yul lha gzhi bdag gi gnod pa thams cad las 'grol bar bar 'gyur ro srog lus dbang thang rlung rta thams cad rgud pa rgyas pa dang zhi rgyas dbang drag 'phrin las bzhi grub 'chi ba med pa'i tshes spel dang tshe bsod dpal sbyor snyan grags zas dang mi nor longs spyod bkra shis phun sum tshogs pa thams cad kyis bskyed par 'gyur ro mi la 'chi 'pho phyugs la god kha zas nor longs spyod la rkye ngan char chad kyi 'jigs pa thams cad mi 'gyur ro 'chi ba med pa tshe ring dpal sbyor gyi bdud rtsi'i @014a * rgyun 'babs pa'i gur kha zhes bya ba 'di <item>

<vol>2798</vol>

'khor gling gi slob dpon bstan 'dzin 'phrin las dang rab 'byams smra ba blo bzang chos grags grwa mang rnams kyis bskul ba la brten nas dang por yongs 'dzin dam pa dkon mchog chos 'phel gyi drung du chos 'di lan kha yar thos pa dang rang 'grel gnyis kyi dgongs pa bstun zhing rang gzhan gyi mkhas pa du ma'i yig cha la zhib tu dpyad de gzhung don rnams ma lus par bkral zhing spyi don dang mtha' bsrel dang nyams yig las yig cha gzhan ma mthong ba dang bye ba ring bsrel de la yang rje dharma swa mi'i gsung gang yin rnams nad thog tu 'gro zhing legs cha shas cher gyur kyang nad rigs mtha' dag <rkts></rkts>
<vol>2923</vol>
<tib>zab mo rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i mtha' dpyod legs par bshad pa'i rgya mtsho zhes bya ba</tib>
<p>1a-259a</p>
<col>@257b ces zab mo rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i mtha' dpyod legs par bshad pa'i rgya mtsho zhes bya ba 'di ni mos dge phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pa'i dga' dams gwa slob snga phyi mang po zhis gis yang nas yang du bskul zhing khyad par du sog po rab 'byams pa blo bzang don grub kyis chos kyi rje thams cad mkhyen pa 'jam dbyangs bla ma'i zhal snga nas kyi ljags rtsom dbu ma'i mtha' spyod rin po che'i stod cha tshad ma dang smad cha yang thal bzlog gi 'jug la nye ba'i bar du rgyug ring phul nas bkra shis kha ngar dri ma med pa dang dngul srang ngar yug dang bcas nas bskul ba la brten nas dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad kyi gsang ba gsum gyi gnas mtha' dag la lgog tu ma 'gyur ba'i spyan dang ldan pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa rigs dang dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi bdag po chos kyi rje thams cad mkhyen pa 'jam dbyangs bzhad pa'i rdo rje'i zhal snga nas kyi zhabs rdul spyi bor blangs nas yun ring bo'i bar du mdo sngags kyi gzhung lugs la sbyangs pa mi dman pa mang du thos pa'i rgyal khams pa sh'akya'i dge slong sdom brtson pa dka' bcu smra ba ngag dbang bkra shis @258a * pa'i dpal gyis chos rje rin po che'i ljags rtsoms kyi yig cha rnams la 'dris par byas nas mngon pa gnyis cha 'brel dang bcas pa dang rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba dang po dang rnam par 'byed pa'i mdo'i 'grel ba dang 'grel bshad gnyis dang 'phags pas lu ljang ba'i mdo'i 'grel ba gnyis la brten nas me 'brug gi lo ston ston zla ba'i yar ngo'i tshes brgyad la chos sde chen po dge ldan bshad sgrub dar rgyas bkra shis kun nas 'khyil ba'i gling du 'jug rdzogs par sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni rab 'byams smra ba grags pa chos 'phel gyis bgyis pa'o 'dis kyang rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che phyogs dus kun tu dar zhing rgyas la yun ring du gnas par gyur cig  swa sti gser sbyangs lhun po'i mtshan dpe'i dpal ngoms zhing 'gro blor gang 'tsham zab rgyas rten 'byung 'doms mkhyen dang brtse ba'i snang byed rtag 'chad na lhun 'grub mdzad ldan ston pa mchog dang mtshungs zab dang rgya che'i rten 'brel bdud rtsi'i btud rmongs pa'i srog 'phrog thad pa'i lus gso ba ma rtog log rtog dri ma sam sbags par thugs brtse'i bum bzang las 'ongs mkhas rnams rgyal thub bstan yongs kyi mnga' bdag tsong kha pa'i dri med rang lugs nyin mo'i dbang phyug ltad tsher gsal snyan rgyud gsang ba'i ja chen bdag bdud bzhi las rgyal 'jam dbyangs @258b bzhad pa rgyal mkhas shing grub pa'i rtser son 'khrungs rabs kyi nor bu'i tog mdzes cod pan rtser bkod nas yab gcig rang bstan bdag por mngar gsol ba dag gi dbang phyug bkra shis zhabs la 'dud mgon de'i legs par bshad pa mi zad mdzod rgya bod gzhung lugs ma lus gsal byed mchog rgol ngan glang po'i glad 'gems gdong lnga pa skal ldan re skong dbang gi rgyal po'ang 'di gnam pa skos bstan 'dzin chos kyi rgyal po yi chos srid zung gi gdung rabs 'dzin pa la sprul pa'i sa skyongs dam pas byin brlabs pa'i chos rgyal dbang phyug shar yab yum gyi mdzad bzang mthu las bar du legs bzhengs pa'i mthun rkyen spyor mkhan dka' bcu bsam 'phel dang phyag mdzod dka' bcu blo bzang chos skyongs gnyis par mkhas dge slong grags pa rgyal mtshos brkos 'di bskrun rnam dgar rang gzhan dge tshogs dang mchog gsum byin brlabs chos dbyings bden pa'i gshis bstan bsrung rgya mtsho'i 'phrin las bsdoms pa'i mthus dbang phyug yab yum sras bcas zhabs brtan cing sku tshe mnga' thang stobs 'byor dbyar mtsho ltar 'phel rgyas bla ma mchog gis 'bral med bu rjes bzung mthar thug don gnyis 'grub gyur cig 'di yi dge bas @259a * mkha' mnyam mar gyur 'gro sgo gsum brtson bgyis kun kyang tshe rabs su theg mchog bshes kyi rjes bzung dal 'byor thog ma nor yongs su rdzogs pa'i bstan pa la thos bsam bsgoms pa ma lus mthar phyin nas kun mkhyen ye shes mchog la spyod par shog legs tshogs rgya mtshos rgyal ba'i mdo sngags kyi bstan pa phyogs dus kun tu dar rgyas zhing khyad par zhwa ser ring lugs dri med kyi snying po mchog 'dis phyogs dus kun khyab shog bstan pa'i 'byung gnas dge ldan bkra shis bde skyong gling du par du legs par bsgrubs pa dge'o "</col>
</item>

<item>

<tib>byin rlabs ches myur ba dpal 'khor lo bde mchog yab yum gyi bsnyen sgrub las gsum gyi skabs nye bar mkho ba'i lag len rim par bsgrigs pa snyan brgyud nor bu'i 'phreng ba dngos grub kun 'byung zhes bya ba bzhugs so dpe 'di ni dbang ma thob cing sngags la ma dad pa lta grub mi mthun pa nga rgyal khengs dregs can sogs la shin tu gsang ba byed dgos pas su rung rung la bston par mi bya'o "</tib>

<item>

<vol>2927</vol>
<tib>gsang ba sngags kyi rig pa 'dzin pa rnams la nye bar mkho ba'i dam tshig gi rdzas dang yo byad kyi rnam bzhag dngos grub gter mdzod ces bya ba</tib>
<p>1a-50b</p>
<col>@050a * ces gsang ba sngags kyi rig pa 'dzin pa rnams la nye bar mkho ba'i dam tshig gi rdzas dang @050b yo byad kyi rnam bzhag dngos grub gter mdzod ces bya ba 'di ni lam 'di'i rnal 'byor sgrub pa po rnams brtul zhugs kyi yan lag 'di dag zhib tu shes pa shin tu gal che bar gsungs pas rang nyid kyi dran gso dang gzhung chen mo rnams kyi dgongs don zab mo re zhig blos 'chun dka' ba'i rigs 'ga' zhig la phan pa'i bsam pas nye bar bskul te mkhas grub thams cad mkhyen pa'i gsung gi bdud rtsi rnal 'byor rol pa'i dga' ston gyi don gyi gtso bo rnams kyi byin brlabs dang dag pa sogs kyi bshad pa logs su dgod pa dang bcas cha lag tshang la gsal zhing go bde bar bla ma dam pa du ma'i bka' drin gyis nye bar 'tsho ba ban rgan snyom las pa ^dam tshig rdo rjes sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni tshul 'di la don gnyer dang ldan zhing rnam dpyod rab tu yongs pa'i slob du dge slong mgron gnyer bkra shis rdo rjes 'bad pas bgyis pa 'dis kyang gsang chen rdo rje theg pa'i lam bzang 'jam mgon bla ma'i ring lugs bla na med pa phyogs dus kun tu dar zhing rgyas pa yun ring du gnas par gyur cig dge legs 'phel "</col>

<tib>'jam mgon snyan brgyud kyi man ngag thun mong ma yin pa dpal 'khor lo sdom pa yab yum gyi bsnyen bsgrub las gsum gyi rnam bzhag gsang chen bcud thig dngos grub nor bu'i gter mdzod zhes bya ba bzhugs so rje gser khang pa'i zhal chab dron mo mkha' 'gro'i snying khrag lta bu 'di nyid dbang ma thob pa dang bla ma la dam sel yod pa dang lta grub mi mthun bsogs dang gsang sngags zab mo dad pa med pa rnams la dpe tsam yang ston par phyed mi rung ngo "</tib>

<col>@015a * zhes 'jam mgon snyan brgyud kyi man ngag thun mong ma yin pa dpal 'khor lo sdom pa yab yum gyi bsnyen sgrub las gsum gyi rnam bzhag nag 'gros su bkod pa gsang chen bcud thig dngos grub nor bu'i gter mdzod ces bya ba 'di yang dad ldan slob bu gser skong sprul sku ngag dbang tshul khrims don ldan nas nan cher yang yang bskul ngor kun mkhyen 'jam dbyangs bzhad pa'i rdo rje dang rje gser khang pa yab sras sogs dam pa snga mas mdzad pa'i bsnyen sgrub kyi yig cha'i skor rnams dang gtso bor bla ma'i gsung gi bdud rtsi ji ltar ba bzhin du dmigs rnams lag len gal che ba thun mong ma pa'o ^rje gser khang pa'i zhal chab dron mo mkha' 'gro'i snying khrag lta bu 'di nyid dbang ma thob pa dang bla ma la dam sel yod pa dang lta grub mi mthun pa sogs la ston pa dang de dag gis blta bsogs byas na bka' sdod gur zhal yab yum las kyi gshin rje rnams kyis snying @015b khrag dron mo zhal du bzhes shing ces bka' rgyas btab pa yin pas bag yod par 'tshal rnam dag tshul khrims ngur smrig sbas par gsal bar yod pas bka' sdod gnas gsum mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams kyis bzod par bzhes la dngos grub rgya mtsho'i char chen phabs ste lam 'di'i rnal 'byor pa rnams bu bzhin du skyong bar mdzod cig gong du bsnyen sgrub sbrags ma'i lha dbang du byed pa'i sbyin sreg sogs kyi skabs bzhad pa brgyad sgrogs pa 'jigs byed la nges gsel du gsungs shing bde gsang rnal 'byor ma rgyal ba rgya mtsho sogs kyi skabs dngos su sgrogs par ma gsal yang bde mchog la bzhad pa brgyad sgrogs kyang mi mthus pa med par ma zad rgyud don dang mthun nam snyam par mkhas pas dpyad 'tshal bsnyen bsgrub las gsum gyi skor 'di rnams rgyud sde bzhi ka la sbyar lugs yod pa rgyud 'grel dang ngags rim sogs tshad ldan gyi gzhung rnams las gsung ba'i 'di nyid kyi khog phub te gzhir gzung nas bde gsang 'khor chen sogs ltar rang rang gi cho ga'i chings dang sngags rnams so sor sbyor tshul shes dgos shing gzhung gong 'og rnams su cung mi 'dra tsam yod pa yang 'gal bar mi sems par rgyud don gyi dgongs pa ltar gnas pa mkhyen par 'tshal 'di ltar bgyis pa'i dge tshogs 'di'i mthus bdag gzhan 'brel thob rnams kyi gtsos mkha' mnyam 'gro kun bla ma he ru ka rje btsun ngag dbang nor bu dpal bzang @016a * pos tshe rabs kun tu 'bral med dgyes bzhin rjes su bzung nas rgyal ba rnams kyi dam chos ma lus pa rgyal ba'i dgongs pa ji lta ba bzhin du 'dzin pa'i rgyur gyur cig bde chen 'phel zhal gro "</col>

<vol>2930</vol>
<tib>no title [@003a * ae ma ho kam ni zag med bde ba che p'a la skyong zhing spel ba'i mchog rang bzhin rnam dag chos kyi dbyings mtshon phyir phyi ni dung ltar dkar ]"</tib>

<tib>rta mgrin gsang sgrub kyi chos skor las rang gzhan la dge mtshan spel ba'i cho ga dge legs rgya mtsho'i char 'bebs zhes bya ba</tib>

</item>

<item>
<rkts></rkts>
<vol>2971</vol>

<tib>dpal phyag na rdo rje gtum po chen po'i sgo nas phyugs la mchod tshul phyugs nor kun 'phel zhes bya ba</tib>

<col>@012a * (ces dpal phyag na rdo rje gtum po chen po'i sgo nas phyugs lha mchod tshul phyugs nor kun 'phel ces bya ba 'di yang yul phyogs 'ga' zhig tu phyugs yams mchod par phan par 'gyur ro snyam nas dge slong gi gzugs can gsang bdag rdo rjes 'phral du mgyogs par sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni dbu mdzad dge slong dpal 'byor don yod do 'dis kyang 'gro ba yongs la phan thogs par gyur cig</col>
</item>

<item>
<rkts></rkts>
<vol>2999</vol>
<tib>ga-yang 'bod yid bzhin 'gugs pa'i lcags kyu</tib>
<p>1a-6a</p>
<col>@004b ces pa 'di ni thos bsam gling gi spyi gnyer dad brtson ldan pa rab 'byams @005a * pa blo bzang dpal ldan gyis grwa tshang gi las don dang 'brel ba'i ga-yang 'bod bya tshul rgyal gsol gyi mjug tu 'don rgyu zhig dgos tshul zer bar dge 'dun spyi'i ga-yang 'bod tshul khrims rnam par dag pa dang sgos su mtshan nyid grwa tshang gi ga-yang 'bod bka' bod lnga'i 'chang nyan sngags grwa rnams kyi ga-yang 'bod rgyud don rim gnyis kyi bshad sgrub 'don phyag len sogs yin gyi ga-yang mgron po 'bod pa bzhin byed pa dka' na'ang rang rang gis rgyu bsgrubs pa'i thog tu rkyen srung ma'i thugs rgyud bskul na phan par bsams te @005b ^btsun pa dkon mchog bstan pa'i sgron mes bris pa'o dpon slob dgon gnas dge 'dun bcas pa yis bsgrub bsgrub bsten pa'i srung ma khyod min pa re sa gzhan na med do brtser dgongs te gzhi lam byes gsum kun tu skyabs mdzod cig nyin gsum 'bod do nyin gyi bya ra mdzod mtshan gsum 'bod do mtshan gyi mel tshe mdzod mi nad phyugs nad kha smras chos rkun sogs mi 'dod nyer 'tshe thams cad phyir zlog cig zas nor longs spyod rkang 'gro rin chen sogs mkho dgu'i 'byor @006a * pa dbyar gyi sprin bzhin 'dus rnam dkar chos kyi bya ba ma lus pa smon pa bzhin du 'grub pa'i sdongs grogs mdzod ces pa 'di yang rje nyid kyi gsung ngo "</col>
</item>
